GIZMO — public repository for Paper 1 (substrate + GIZMO framework)

This repository's contents fall under two licenses:

1. SUBSTRATE + DERIVED ANALYTICAL OUTPUTS — CC-BY 4.0
   --------------------------------------------------
   - `substrate/graph.json` — the 38,148-node GIZMO biochemistry substrate.
   - `figures/` — manuscript figures and source TSVs.
   - `results/` — per-cohort manuscript-source tables.
   - Per-cohort case-study bundles (deposited at Zenodo on acceptance).

